@startuml

actor Administrator
actor Student
actor Instructor
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Enrollment Service" as EnrollSvc
database "Relational Database" as DB
participant "University Student\nInformation System" as SIS
participant "Email & Notification\nService" as Notify

' Login & Navigation Phase
== Login & Navigation ==
Administrator -> UI: Enter Credentials
activate UI
UI -> API: POST /auth/login
activate API
API -> DB: Verify user credentials
activate DB
DB --> API: User record + role
deactivate DB
API --> UI: 200 OK + Auth Token
deactivate API
Administrator -> UI: Navigate to Enrollment Management
Administrator -> UI: Search student (by name or ID)
UI -> API: GET /users?role=student&query={searchTerm}
activate API
API -> EnrollSvc: searchStudents(query)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: Query student records by name or ID
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: Matching student records
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: Student list
deactivate EnrollSvc
API --> UI: Display student results
deactivate API
Administrator -> UI: Select student from results
Administrator -> UI: Browse available course offerings
UI -> API: GET /courses?status=active
activate API
API -> EnrollSvc: getCourseOfferings()
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: Query active course offerings
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: Course records with seat counts
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: Course offerings list
deactivate EnrollSvc
API --> UI: Display available courses
deactivate API
Administrator -> UI: Select target course
deactivate UI

' Prerequisite Check Phase
== Prerequisite Check ==
UI -> API: GET /students/{studentId}/academic-record
activate UI
activate API
API -> EnrollSvc: getAcademicRecord(studentId)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> SIS: fetchAcademicRecord(studentId)
activate SIS
SIS --> EnrollSvc: Student academic record
deactivate SIS
EnrollSvc -> DB: Query course prerequisites for courseId
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: Prerequisite list
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: Academic record + prerequisite check result
deactivate EnrollSvc
API --> UI: Display academic record & prerequisite status
deactivate API

alt Prerequisites Not Met
    UI --> Administrator: Display missing prerequisites
    alt Administrator Overrides Prerequisites
        Administrator -> UI: Log override justification
        UI -> API: POST /enrollments/override
        activate API
        API -> EnrollSvc: logOverride(adminId, studentId, courseId, justification)
        activate EnrollSvc
        EnrollSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO enrollment_overrides (adminId, studentId, courseId, justification)
        activate DB
        DB --> EnrollSvc: OK
        deactivate DB
        EnrollSvc --> API: Override logged
        deactivate EnrollSvc
        API --> UI: 201 Override recorded
        deactivate API
    else Administrator Cancels Enrollment
        UI --> Administrator: Enrollment cancelled
        deactivate UI
    end
end

' Seat Availability Phase
== Seat Availability Check ==
UI -> API: GET /courses/{courseId}/availability
activate UI
activate API
API -> EnrollSvc: checkSeatAvailability(courseId)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: SELECT availableSeats FROM courses WHERE courseId
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: Available seat count
deactivate DB
alt No Seats Available
    EnrollSvc --> API: 409 Course Full
    deactivate EnrollSvc
    API --> UI: Display "Course Full" message
    deactivate API
    alt Add to Waitlist
        Administrator -> UI: Confirm add to waitlist
        UI -> API: POST /courses/{courseId}/waitlist
        activate API
        API -> EnrollSvc: addToWaitlist(studentId, courseId)
        activate EnrollSvc
        EnrollSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO waitlist (studentId, courseId, queuePosition)
        activate DB
        DB --> EnrollSvc: waitlistId
        deactivate DB
        EnrollSvc --> API: 201 Added to waitlist
        deactivate EnrollSvc
        API --> UI: Student added to waitlist
        deactivate API
        API -> Notify: sendWaitlistNotification(studentId, courseId)
        activate Notify
        Notify --> Student: Waitlist confirmation notification
        deactivate Notify
        alt Seat Freed
            EnrollSvc -> DB: Monitor waitlist — seat freed event
            activate EnrollSvc
            activate DB
            DB --> EnrollSvc: Next waitlisted student
            deactivate DB
            EnrollSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO enrollments (studentId, courseId)
            activate DB
            DB --> EnrollSvc: enrollmentId
            deactivate DB
            EnrollSvc --> API: Auto-enrolled from waitlist
            deactivate EnrollSvc
        end
    else Do Not Waitlist
        UI --> Administrator: Enrollment cancelled
        deactivate UI
    end
end

' Enrollment Phase
== Enrollment ==
UI -> API: POST /enrollments
activate UI
activate API
API -> EnrollSvc: enrollStudent(studentId, courseId, adminId)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO enrollments (studentId, courseId, enrolledAt, enrolledBy)
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: enrollmentId
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc -> DB: UPDATE courses SET availableSeats = availableSeats - 1 WHERE courseId
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: OK
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: 201 Enrollment created
deactivate EnrollSvc
API -> SIS: POST /sync/enrollment (studentId, courseId, enrollmentId)
activate SIS
SIS --> API: 200 Sync Confirmed
deactivate SIS
API --> UI: Enrollment Completed
deactivate API
deactivate UI

' Notification & Audit Phase
== Notification & Audit ==
API -> Notify: sendEnrollmentConfirmation(studentId, courseId)
activate Notify
Notify --> Student: Enrollment confirmation email
deactivate Notify
API -> EnrollSvc: updateCourseRoster(courseId, studentId)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: UPDATE course_roster SET students WHERE courseId
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: OK
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: Roster updated
deactivate EnrollSvc
API -> EnrollSvc: logAuditTrail(adminId, action="ENROLL", studentId, courseId)
activate EnrollSvc
EnrollSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO audit_log (adminId, action, studentId, courseId, timestamp)
activate DB
DB --> EnrollSvc: OK
deactivate DB
EnrollSvc --> API: Audit logged
deactivate EnrollSvc

Student -> UI: Access course dashboard & materials
activate UI
UI -> API: GET /courses/{courseId}/dashboard
activate API
API -> DB: Fetch course materials and info
activate DB
DB --> API: Course dashboard data
deactivate DB
API --> UI: Display course dashboard
deactivate API
Instructor -> UI: View updated course roster
UI -> API: GET /courses/{courseId}/roster
activate API
API -> DB: Fetch updated course roster
activate DB
DB --> API: Updated roster
deactivate DB
API --> UI: Display updated course roster
deactivate API
deactivate UI

@enduml
